\id 1TH - Uare
\h 1Tesalonika
\toc3 1Tes
\toc2 1Tesalonika
\toc1 Tesalonika Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\mt1 1Tesalonika
\mt2 Tesalonika Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Pauloꞌa Korinto zamaḡano Tesalonika ekalesia veize mirihiro. Tesalonikaꞌe Makedonia habaꞌano ne boro ꞌahoga. Ibite Pauloꞌa Tesalonika dubu ḡadaheniro, rehano Iuda azaḡa nuꞌa ani mae bunadu ani Berea neḡa onamiro ebu hena Korinto onamiro. Vesu Timoteoꞌa ani vaḡe onamadu Tesalonika ekalesia hariḡa meꞌodoharo. Pauloꞌa hari eꞌe egadu matuꞌiro, mazaḡa ze ꞌize Iesu mazao fiꞌe radiunu. Rehano Iuda azaḡa nuꞌa ze sausauzinuteꞌe uꞌano, zeꞌa aduga zamaḡano edau gigaranoga veize Pauloꞌa soꞌa ꞌahi mirihadu inaraziro. Ebu Iesuꞌa bare ariteꞌe moneo ihoziro.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Eḡe, Paulo zu Silasi ebu Timoteoꞌa Tesalonika ekalesia veize soꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe. Zaꞌe Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso mone azaḡa. Badiꞌaꞌa zae mazao manoḡa zu zama roḡeḡa ziniꞌenoꞌi. \fig Paulo duḡuruꞌa kurauꞌohe|src="AP-14-02.tif" size="col" ref="1:2"\fig*
\s1 Tesalonika Ekalesia uꞌano Badiꞌa mazao Manoḡa Tauḡi rae Reiro
\p 
\v 2 Emeꞌe zae niduꞌa uꞌano iḡaiḡa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe, ebu emeḡe kuru zamaḡano iḡaiḡa zae veize kurauꞌohe.
\v 3 Emeꞌa Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama mazao kurauꞌetene, zae moneo iḡaiḡa ꞌahige zamareꞌohe: Zaeꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌenaꞌa gaueꞌohe, zu vaze zamare borofadu gau boro haḡaeꞌohe, ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa bare ariteꞌe mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa guhineꞌeteꞌe uꞌano zamaze obone giganeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 4 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zamare borofeꞌohe. Emeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zae ohotirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 5 Emeꞌa ḡoere isoḡa hina daꞌo hari manoḡa mene haramoziro, rehano Badiꞌa inaraḡa hina Vine Zaḡoḡa teite haramoziro, ebu emeḡe haramoꞌe huga rae zamare huneꞌenaꞌa, haramoziro. Zaꞌe emeꞌa zae teite radiunuteꞌe zamaḡano zae veize nougenouge radirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 6 Zaꞌe aduga boro hidiroteꞌea Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa matuꞌu zenadu matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa hari manoḡa mae ḡihiniro. ꞌOugadu zaꞌe emeḡe zu Zuhiꞌa Boro tuhutuhufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reiro.
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo Makedonia zu Akaia habaꞌano ekalesia azaḡa niduꞌa zae hari egadu zae tuhutuhuziꞌuma raꞌohe.
\v 8 Mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡoereꞌe zae mazaonoꞌo bororanadu Makedonia zu Akaia habaꞌano daꞌo mene, rehano habaꞌahabaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano vaze niduꞌa zaeꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe hariḡa ederiro. Eꞌanoꞌo emeꞌe zae hariꞌe mene bare reꞌuma,
\v 9 mazaḡa ze zeḡeꞌa bare zae moneo meꞌodofiro. Ze emeꞌa zae vaḡe amirotene zaeꞌa nougenouge emeḡe mae zoufiroteꞌe meꞌodofiro. Ebu zaeꞌa nougenouge ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa modadu Badiꞌa vaḡe ariroteꞌe zu ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa huga veize gaueꞌeteꞌe meꞌodofiro.
\v 10 Ebu za Badiꞌaꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡaboniroteꞌe vazeḡa, ane Ubuga, Iesuꞌa adureonoꞌo bare ovaiteꞌe guhineꞌeteꞌe zeḡeꞌa meꞌodofiro. Iesuꞌe zama moneo ariteꞌe vazeḡa zu Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌanonoꞌo emeḡe ḡabofiteꞌe vazeḡa.
\c 2
\s1 Tesalonikao Pauloꞌa Haḡairoteꞌe Gauḡa
\p 
\v 1 Nego nabudi, za edeḡa, emeḡeꞌa zae vaḡe amirotaꞌaꞌe mene foure reiro.
\v 2 Za edeḡa, ibite Filipo zamaḡano vazeꞌa aduga rifiro zu emeḡe rae sausaufiro, rehano emeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa inarafeadu agire boro bagaḡa zamaḡano zuni Badiꞌa hari manoḡa zae mazao rae fureniro.
\v 3 Mazaḡa emeꞌe zamarone veꞌoḡa ga zama toraga hina mene haramoziniꞌohe ebu zae soꞌozifine mene ḡorezeꞌohe.
\v 4 Rehano emeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ane gau azaḡano ohofadu aniꞌa rifiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa ziꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo emeꞌe mene vaze matuꞌozenoga, rehano Badiꞌa matuꞌohanoga veize harameꞌohe. Badiꞌaꞌe emeḡe zama faifaine ḡianeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 5 Za edeḡa, emeꞌa zamaze auꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hina mene haramido ebu zae mazaonoꞌo manoḡa mouga radu mene soꞌoze ḡorezido. Aꞌe huga rae Badiꞌaꞌa rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 6 Ebu emeꞌe vazeꞌa nigufoga veize mene inariro. Zaeꞌa ga vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoganiꞌa nigufoga mene uratiro.
\v 7 Emeꞌe Keriso apostolo azaḡa radu zae tuḡutuḡuzogaꞌe idaḡa, rehano emeꞌa zae boꞌaḡano radiunutene, viꞌaniꞌa ubugaubuga taufeꞌeteꞌe teige, zae mazao roḡeru haḡainu.
\p 
\v 8 Eme zae zamare borofiro ꞌahine, matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa hari manoḡa zae teite dainihi rae reiro. Mene eꞌe daꞌo, ḡabonefe zuni zae veize matuꞌe ahetihi rae reiro. Mazaḡa zaꞌe emeꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reiro.
\v 9 Nego nabudi, za emeḡeꞌa ḡihau gauirotaꞌaꞌe hube hune zamareꞌohe. Emeꞌa Badiꞌa hari manoḡa zae haramozinuteꞌea, zae boꞌaḡano vazeni ꞌahoga mene aduadunifine ohere zu madai gauinu.
\p 
\v 10 Zaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa radu emeꞌa nougenouge zae mazao haḡairotaꞌaꞌe zaꞌe deheru edereꞌohe, ebu Badiꞌa zuni edereꞌohe. Emeꞌe zae mazao hube hune haḡai deheḡa zu duduḡa haḡairo zu veꞌoḡa mene haḡairo.
\v 11 Zaꞌe edeḡa, moganiꞌa ubugaubuga mazao haḡaeꞌeteꞌe teige, emeꞌe zae tibatiba mazao ꞌouge haḡairo.
\v 12 Emeꞌa zae inaraziro, namiziro zu iraduguziro. Aꞌe, zaeꞌa Badiꞌa matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡae radifine raꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa hina zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa rouga veize huziro.
\p 
\v 13 Emeꞌe iḡaiḡa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe. Mazaḡa emeḡeꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere haramozenadu zaeꞌa mae ḡihinirotene, aꞌe mene vaze ḡoere, rehano hube hune Badiꞌa ḡoere rae mae ḡihiniro. Eꞌe ḡoeꞌa zuni fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, zae zamao gaueꞌohe.
\v 14 Nego nabudi, Iudea habaꞌano Badiꞌa mone ekalesia, Keriso Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao fureraroteꞌeꞌa zae mazao zuni fureraro. Zeḡeꞌa Iuda azaḡa mazaonoꞌo hidiroteꞌe adugaḡaꞌe zae zuni zae teite ḡoere ḡumu azaḡa mazaonoꞌo hidiro.
\v 15 Iuda azaḡaniꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu zu peroveta azaḡa zimiro, ebu emeḡe hegofe bufiro. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa mene matuꞌohauꞌohe zu vaze niduꞌa agiroziꞌohe.
\v 16 Iuda azaḡaꞌe emeꞌa Iuda mene azaḡa haramozenadu ze ḡabone hidoga garareꞌohe. Deꞌugeꞌenaꞌa, ze iḡaiḡa haḡaize sauꞌa ragateragate teadu haḡaize sauꞌa niduꞌaꞌe iriꞌaveꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌaniꞌa zeḡe mazao fureraro.
\s1 Pauloꞌa Tesalonika Ekalesia Ḡiazoga Urateꞌohe
\p 
\v 17 Nego nabudi, emeꞌa mada tahiḡa zae muhize iḡunirotene, ahirio zae mene ḡiaziro rehano, zamafeo iḡaiḡa zae zamariro. Ebu zae ḡiazoga urate rudaunu ꞌahine, zae vaḡe bare amoga radu ibi vaḡe arinu.
\v 18 Eꞌanoꞌo eme zae vaḡe amihi reiro. Hube hune eḡe, Pauloꞌa barebare ibi vaḡiro rehano, Sataniꞌa emeḡe ibi ꞌuiro.
\v 19 Eme uraꞌe bare ḡiazihi raꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌa mazao fie gigaruꞌeꞌuma, onamo emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano emeḡe niduꞌa ane zamao edaꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano emeꞌe zae uꞌano matuꞌiꞌuma ebu zaꞌe emeꞌa Iesu ubumao niguzadu zaꞌe aniꞌa rifiteꞌe kini vadiga adiriḡa teigiꞌuma.
\v 20 Hube hune zaꞌe emeꞌa niguzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu zae uꞌano eme matuꞌeꞌohe.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Eme ꞌouge faḡa guhiu radoga mene idararotene, emeḡe daꞌo Atena zamaḡano radiꞌuma rae zamariro,
\v 2 ebu Timoteoꞌe zae vaḡe tuḡuniro. Aniꞌe emeḡe nego zu Keriso hari manoḡa haramifine emeḡe teite Badiꞌa gau haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌa amine, zae inaraziꞌuma zu zaeꞌa fie gigaranoga veize danaziꞌuma.
\v 3 ꞌOugine, za ꞌuguḡa aduga hideꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zamazeꞌa mene hagariꞌuma. Zaꞌe edere huneꞌohe, fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, emeḡe niduꞌa aduga ꞌuguḡa hube hune hidiꞌuma.
\v 4 Eme zae teite radiunuteꞌe zamaḡano emeḡe niduꞌa aduga hidiꞌuma rae irina ziro, ebu izidi zaꞌe edeḡa, eꞌe aduganiꞌa fureraro.
\v 5 Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌa faḡa guhiu radoga mene idararotene, zaeꞌa nougenouge fieꞌeteꞌe ederoga veize Timoteo tuḡuniro. E Sataniꞌa ibi nunuo zae soꞌozadu emeḡeꞌa zae veize gaue arirotaꞌaꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa reꞌuma rae riharo.
\s1 Timoteoꞌa Tesalonika Ekalesia moneo Hari Manoḡa Odohe Ariro
\p 
\v 6 Rehano Timoteoꞌa izidi zae mazaonoꞌo emeḡe vaḡe bare aradu zaeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe zu zamarotiteꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡa meꞌodofiro. Ebu zaꞌa matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa iḡaiḡa emeḡe zamareꞌeteꞌe ihofiro, zu emeḡeꞌa ḡiaze hunihi raꞌeteꞌe teige, zae zuni ḡiafe hunihi raꞌeteꞌe ihofiro.
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo, nego nabudi, eme aduga zu sauꞌa hideꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zuni zaeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano zamafeꞌa inariro.
\v 8 Zaeꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro teite tiburanadu edau gigaruꞌe ꞌahine, izidi emeꞌa matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, ḡabode radiuꞌohe.
\v 9 Emeꞌa zae uꞌano Badiꞌa mazao ufeta manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe, mazaḡa zae uꞌano emeꞌa emeḡe Badiꞌa zamao matuꞌu niduꞌa meiro.
\v 10 Eme zae bare ḡiazoga veize zu zaeꞌa fie gigarafine danazoga veize, ohere zu madai niduꞌa ufeta inare kurauꞌohe.
\p 
\v 11 Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa eme zae vaḡe amiteꞌe ibiḡa mae bohanifine, kurauꞌohe.
\v 12 Ebu emeḡeꞌa zae zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, zaezaeꞌa zamarotitoga veize zu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa danazadu vaze zamare borofoga veize kurauꞌohe.
\v 13 Ebu aniꞌa zamaze inaraneadu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa ane mone azaḡa niduꞌa teite ovaiteꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama ubumao veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa zu zaḡoḡa rouga veize kurauꞌohe.
\c 4
\s1 Badiꞌa Matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe Ḡaboneḡa
\p 
\v 1 Ḡonagano, nego nabudi, emeꞌa ibite Badiꞌa matuꞌohafine nougenouge raditeꞌe moneo ihoziro, ebu zaꞌe ꞌouge radiuꞌohe. Izidi eme zaeꞌa ufeta ꞌouge haḡae radoga veize Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano umizeꞌohe zu inaraziꞌohe.
\v 2 Mazaḡa zaꞌe edeḡa, emeꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu niḡano nagi ihoreḡa ziniro.
\v 3 Badiꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa zaḡozaḡe radoga urateꞌohe. Zaꞌe mene daro futaꞌuma,
\v 4 zae tibatibaꞌa zaḡozaḡe zu gubaneꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano nougenouge ahirize\f + \fr 4:4 \fqa ize \f* taufeꞌeteꞌe ederiꞌuma,
\v 5 Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa, mene Iuda azaḡa teige, ubuma gezo mene haḡaiꞌuma,
\v 6 ebu ꞌuguḡa haḡaiḡa nego nabudi mazao haḡadu mene mae veꞌoziꞌuma zu sausauziꞌuma. Emeꞌa amahi zae ziroteꞌe zu riḡa iraduguziroteꞌe teige, Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa haḡai ꞌuguḡa niduꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aduga ziniꞌuma.
\v 7 Eme toragano mene radifine, rehano zaḡozaḡe ḡabode radifine Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe hufiro.
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo ihore ꞌadi hezahohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene vaze hezahohauꞌohe, rehano Vine Zaḡoḡa ziniꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa hezahohauꞌohe.
\p 
\v 9 U nego nabudi zamarotitoga moneoꞌe emeꞌa mirihozenoga mene urateꞌohe, mazaḡa za zaeꞌa bare Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo zamarotiteꞌeteꞌe ihoreḡa meiro.
\v 10 Ebu hube hune zaꞌe Makedonia habaꞌano nego nabudi niduꞌa zamare borofeꞌohe. Rehano, nego nabudi, emeꞌa bare umizeꞌohe, “Za ufeta zamarotitoꞌi.”
\v 11 Ebu emeꞌa zae ziroteꞌe idunaḡano roḡeru radifine inaroꞌi, zae gau faine zamareꞌenaꞌa ḡihau gauoꞌi, ebu ꞌevoreze hina gaue radoꞌi.
\v 12 ꞌOugine, mene fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa zae gubaziꞌuma, zu ferezeꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa radu vaze mazao ḡau ꞌahoga mene umidiꞌuma.
\s1 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Bare Ariꞌuma
\p 
\v 13 Nego nabudi, eme zaeꞌa rune azaḡa moneo ederoga urateꞌohe. Mene fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe runeonoꞌo mene bare ḡabodiꞌuma rae zamaradu zamaze areꞌohe. Rehano zaꞌe mene zeḡe teigiꞌuma.
\v 14 Eme Iesuꞌa rudanadu bare ḡabodiroteꞌe mae ḡihineꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa bare ovaiteꞌe madaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa iniu Iesu mazao fiadu rudaroteꞌe azaḡa zuni Iesu teite zamaziꞌuma.
\v 15 Emeḡeꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡoere ziꞌohe. Eme ḡabode radiꞌuma onamo Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ovaiꞌuma, rehano ibite rudaroteꞌe azaḡa mene vitiziꞌuma.
\v 16 Zuhiꞌa Boro aneꞌa bare adureonoꞌo ovaiteꞌe madaḡano, aniꞌe ḡoere riḡa ḡihau huaꞌuma, ebu tuḡure viga ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa huaꞌuma zu Badiꞌa bigoro hudiꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano Keriso mazao fiadu rudaroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ibite geno ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma.
\v 17 Eꞌe enogano eme, ꞌize ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe teite idaḡa mae ḡihifadu ḡoze zamaḡano diuḡiꞌuma ebu adureo Zuhiꞌa Boro hidiꞌuma. Ebu emeꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro teite radiꞌuma, onamo tuḡutuḡu.
\v 18 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe ḡoere ꞌahiguḡa hina inaratitoꞌi.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Nego nabudi, Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe zae veize mene mirihiꞌuma.
\v 2 Mazaḡa za edeḡa hune, Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaꞌe ḡonoreꞌa ohere areꞌeteꞌe teigiꞌuma.
\v 3 Vazeꞌa raenaꞌa, “Emeꞌe uniho manoḡano sauꞌa ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa radiuꞌohe,” rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano aduga boroꞌa feuradu ze tabara ruiziꞌuma. Aꞌe roḡae ahiꞌetaniꞌa ene furenoga radu gigiꞌaniꞌa feurohuꞌeteꞌe teigiꞌuma. Ebu zeꞌe aduga boro eꞌe mode feranoga mene idaraꞌuma.
\p 
\v 4 Rehano nego nabudi, zaꞌe mene uzabo zamaḡano radiuꞌe ꞌahine, Iesuꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ḡonore teige aradu za mene zaguzaguziꞌuma.
\v 5 Zae niduꞌa madai zu agaḡa zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa. Emeꞌe ohere zu uzabo zamaḡano mene radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.
\v 6 Eꞌanoꞌo emeꞌe bazeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mene teigiꞌuma, rehano evateꞌenaꞌa, tohutohe radiꞌuma.
\v 7 Mazaḡa bazeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ohereo bazeꞌohe ebu gagone fuꞌa azaḡaꞌe ohereo gage futauꞌohe.
\v 8 Rehano emeꞌe madai zamaḡano radiuꞌe ꞌahine, tohutohe radiꞌuma. Ebu fieꞌenaꞌa zamarotitiꞌuma, aꞌe utio ꞌuꞌuni biriḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Ebu ḡabone hidiꞌuma rae mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa guhiniꞌuma, aꞌe uti karaḡauḡa haḡadu vadini bireꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.
\v 9 Badiꞌaꞌe zamaḡa ḡugiꞌa hina aduga rififine emeḡe mene ohotiro, rehano emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Keriso uꞌano ḡabone hidifine ohotiro.
\v 10 Kerisoꞌa emeḡe veize rudaro. Aꞌe emeꞌa ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe ga rudaroteꞌe zamaḡano ani teite radoga veize raꞌohe.
\v 11 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe inaratitoꞌi ebu danatitoꞌi. Izidi hube hune zaeꞌa ꞌouge haḡaeꞌeteꞌe teige, ꞌouge haḡaeꞌenoꞌi.
\s1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa Ḡonaga
\p 
\v 12 Nego nabudi, eme umizeꞌohe. Zae boꞌaḡano gau boro haḡaeꞌenaꞌa, Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡoere idunaḡano zae ibitoziꞌeteꞌe zu ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa gubazoꞌi.
\v 13 Zeḡeꞌa zae veize gaueꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ze zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa zamaze niduꞌa hina gubazoꞌi. Zaezae niduꞌa uniho manoḡa zamaḡano radoꞌi.
\v 14 Nego nabudi, eme umizeꞌohe. Tubuḡa azaḡaꞌe riḡa iraduguzoꞌi, rihauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe inarazoꞌi, zoreḡa azaḡaꞌe danazoꞌi, ebu vaze niduꞌa mazao zamaze obone giganoꞌi.
\v 15 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahoga mazao sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, sauꞌa hina ago naenaenoꞌi, rehano zae boꞌaḡano zu vaze niduꞌa mazao iḡaiḡa manoḡa haḡaoꞌi.
\v 16 Mada niduꞌa matuꞌe radoꞌi.
\v 17 Iḡaiḡa kuranoꞌi.
\v 18 Naginiꞌa fureranoꞌidene zuni, Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi roꞌi. Eꞌeguḡa niduꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa zae mazaonoꞌo urateꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa.
\v 19 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa zae mazao gaueꞌeteꞌe ago ꞌuoꞌi.
\v 20 Badiꞌaꞌa ihozadu rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ago reꞌoreꞌone modoꞌi.
\v 21 Ḡau niduꞌa tuhune ḡianoꞌi. Manoḡa ḡauḡa obone giganoꞌi.
\v 22 Sauꞌa nunuonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.
\p 
\v 23 Emeꞌe zama roḡeḡa rifiꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa aneꞌa ḡau niduꞌa moneo zae mae zaḡozaḡozifine kurauꞌohe. Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa danazadu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano vineze zu ahirizeꞌe veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa radifine kurauꞌohe.
\v 24 Zae huziroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡaꞌe zamaḡa niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, aniꞌa hube hune ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 25 Nego nabudi, emeḡe veize kuranoꞌi.
\p 
\v 26 Nego nabudi niduꞌa kavarotiteꞌenaꞌa, unihotitoꞌi.
\v 27 Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano ḡoere riḡa ziꞌohe. Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe nego nabudi niduꞌa veize meꞌodoꞌi.
\p 
\v 28 Emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa zae mazao manoḡa fureneꞌenoꞌi. 
